{"tid":2031924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民間智慧] 集思廣益齊抗共","createTime":"2020-05-23T17:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T03:29:30.000Z","uid":93479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a489a572269e53512bdc1ba322608e93a15326","tid":2031924,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"唔好話我on9 膠化, 仲信法治，over my dead body<br />\n唔好失敗主義，做得幾多得幾多，你行得出嚟就即係仲信上街係有用<br />\n<br />\n同支共就係鬥嗱喳鬥爛鬥嚟橫折曲，以其人之道還治其人之身<br />\n<br />\n1, 共同目的而聚集<br />\n搵張支那國旗 ，印出嚟/ save 落電話，出到港島對搵個有日期時間地方(黨鐵站) 拎住中國國旗打張卡。 預左畀人票控上庭抗辯做理據<br />\n<br />\n2， 有鏡頭影住即刻唱國歌，之後可以呈堂表明在場目的<br />\n<br />\n3，打砸搶？揸住國旗唱住紅歌仲係咪黑暴？<br />\n<br />\n有咁奇情就咁奇情，就係要你班毅進爛仔你班港共垃圾反應唔嚟"},{"pid":"999745bd2b4aba9dc618772159b988c5406641c5","tid":2031924,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:51:10.000Z","msg":"【致所有送頭論的同路人】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031917</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"28c8bc6d8ca279b0faebff31d66043c27f6cb5a0","tid":2031924,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LF6k6T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LF6k6T.png&h=830c19f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>銅鑼灣 商務大減價<br />\n<br />\n大家袋定響手機 524去打書釘</strong></span>"},{"pid":"cf50e230fc6c913fe6e99557752f0a94299869b7","tid":2031924,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:04:31.000Z","msg":"【致所有送頭論的同路人】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031917</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c2c16a139d6e8164acb486c4921862c4d4710ea2","tid":2031924,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:51:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80546bd1bdc189ff147570c7500eab72d54d7636","tid":2031924,"uid